and the door hit my eye.

41
00:06:04,291 --> 00:06:05,374
You're right.

42
00:06:05,458 --> 00:06:07,040
I'm really stupid.

43
00:06:08,458 --> 00:06:09,374
So, I was saying,

44
00:06:09,458 --> 00:06:13,915
Shakti Kumaarr was so mean
that the poor kid broke down.

45
00:06:16,541 --> 00:06:17,999
I am right.

46
00:06:18,875 --> 00:06:20,582
You really are stupid.

47
