Two chocolates?

53
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:14,457
No.

54
00:07:14,541 --> 00:07:15,457
One chocolate?

55
00:07:15,791 --> 00:07:16,874
Shut up.

56
00:07:16,958 --> 00:07:17,874
Not even one?

57
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,999
- No!
- Insia!

58
00:07:20,166 --> 00:07:22,499
Have you no manners?

59
00:07:22,583 --> 00:07:24,290
Haven't greeted me?

60
00:07:24,416 --> 00:07:25,707
May peace be on you, grand-aunt.

61
00:07:25,791 --> 00:07:28,207
May peace be on you, too.

62
00:07:28,291 --> 00:07:29,665
Why didn't you get me a gift?

63
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:30,749
Get out of here!

64
00:07:30,833 --> 00:07:31,957
Gift... gift. Go!

65
00:07:32,041 --> 00:07:35,207
Why are you screaming at my Guddu?

66
00:07:35,416 --> 00:07:39,124
- Guddu...
- Up to no good, this mother and daughter!

67
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:45,707
This one... no this one...

68
