Good job.

69
00:08:03,541 --> 00:08:05,540
So, judges, what's your verdict?

70
00:08:05,625 --> 00:08:06,832
Monali-ji?

71
00:08:06,916 --> 00:08:08,249
Aw, you're so cute.

72
00:08:08,333 --> 00:08:10,624
- 1 0 points just for cuteness.
- Wow, 1 0 points!

73
00:08:10,708 --> 00:08:11,749
What?

74
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:12,832
Cuteness?

75
00:08:13,041 --> 00:08:14,374
Are we judging cuteness?

76
00:08:14,583 --> 00:08:16,124
This is a singing show, Monali.

77
00:08:16,208 --> 00:08:16,999
Singing.

78
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:19,374
I know my job. I'm a judge, too.

79
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:20,540
You're a rubbish judge.

80
00:08:20,625 --> 00:08:22,415
He can't sing to save his life.

81
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:26,082
Kiddo, you're an insult to talent!

82
00:08:26,166 --> 00:08:28,624
You're an insult to talent!

83
00:08:28,708 --> 00:08:29,540
How dare you!

84
00:08:29,625 --> 00:08:30,749
What do you know about talent?

85
00:08:30,833 --> 00:08:31,915
Don't interrupt.

86
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,165
What are you looking at?

87
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:34,374
Now, get out!

88
00:08:34,541 --> 00:08:36,165
Get out!

89
