on a hot summer day."

541
00:41:00,250 --> 00:41:09,040
"She's like a warm blanket,
on a freezing winter night."

542
00:41:09,208 --> 00:41:13,540
"My dearest mom."

543
00:41:13,750 --> 00:41:18,165
"She's my dearest... my mom."

544
00:41:18,375 --> 00:41:22,582
