"O my heart, stop insisting."

1652
01:56:15,791 --> 01:56:24,874
"Lock your cage from within,
along with your dreams."

1653
01:56:26,791 --> 01:56:29,165
Kiddo, I've spoken to Sheena.

1654
01:56:29,250 --> 01:56:30,082
There are many ways.

1655
01:56:30,166 --> 01:56:31,457
You can lodge a complaint with the police.

1656
01:56:31,541 --> 01:56:33,332
There's a children's organization here
which can help you.

1657
01:56:33,416 --> 01:56:34,290
There's Sheena. There's me.

1658
01:56:34,375 --> 01:56:36,624
You don't need to waste your life.

1659
01:56:36,708 --> 01:56:39,540
Sir, my mom didn't give up on me.

1660
01:56:40,041 --> 01:56:41,707
She fought for me.

1661
01:56:42,208 --> 01:56:43,915
It's my turn now.

1662
01:56:44,083 --> 01:56:45,707
How can I desert her?

1663
01:56:45,958 --> 01:56:46,999
But...

1664
01:56:47,375 --> 01:56:48,374
what about you, Insia?

1665
01:56:48,666 --> 01:56:50,249
Why are you wasting your talent?

1666
