1741
02:01:47,000 --> 02:01:49,915
- Best Singer.
- What? Really?

1742
02:01:50,166 --> 02:01:51,040
And me, too.

1743
02:01:51,083 --> 02:01:51,874
Wow, sir.

1744
02:01:51,916 --> 02:01:53,165
I can't believe it.

1745
02:01:53,333 --> 02:01:54,374
When is it?

1746
02:01:54,458 --> 02:01:57,249
On the 20th. In Mumbai. You should come.

1747
02:01:58,041 --> 02:01:58,957
No, sir.

1748
02:01:59,041 --> 02:02:01,457
I won't be able to come. You know that.

1749
02:02:01,708 --> 02:02:03,832
But, you will surely win the award.

1750
02:02:04,500 --> 02:02:06,082
Ha! Fat chance.

1751
02:02:06,291 --> 02:02:08,040
No, sir. Don't say that.

1752
02:02:08,166 --> 02:02:09,749
You'll surely win.

1753
02:02:11,250 --> 02:02:12,624
Listen.

1754
02:02:14,458 --> 02:02:16,624
Don't forget about me when you go to Saudi.

1755
02:02:18,250 --> 02:02:19,332
Keep in touch.

1756
02:02:19,708 --> 02:02:21,832
How can I forget you?

1757
02:02:22,333 --> 02:02:24,207
You've done so much for me.

1758
02:02:24,458 --> 02:02:26,374
- Thank you.
- God bless, kiddo.

1759
02:02:26,500 --> 02:02:27,790
God bless.

1760
02:02:34,000 --> 02:02:35,457
Don't be sad.

1761
02:02:35,583 --> 02:02:37,540
You are anyway the best singer.

1762
02:02:38,166 --> 02:02:39,790
And you, best friend.

1763
02:02:39,875 --> 02:02:41,082
Thank you.

1764
02:02:43,125 --> 02:02:44,457
Let's celebrate today?

1765
