How was the exam?

1790
02:05:30,416 --> 02:05:31,749
Good.

1791
02:05:32,833 --> 02:05:34,624
I'm going to Mumbai.

1792
02:05:34,708 --> 02:05:36,540
For the Glamour Awards.

1793
02:05:36,750 --> 02:05:38,999
Shakti sir has kept a pass for me.

1794
02:05:42,416 --> 02:05:44,457
I'll miss you, Chintan.

1795
02:05:45,541 --> 02:05:46,582
I'll miss you, too.

1796
02:05:46,666 --> 02:05:52,165
