He'll be back in two minutes.

1808
02:07:02,333 --> 02:07:04,249
No problem. Please step out of the queue.

1809
02:07:04,333 --> 02:07:05,624
No... please check these.

1810
02:07:05,708 --> 02:07:08,249
Mom, don't worry. I'll take care of it.

1811
02:07:09,000 --> 02:07:10,749
From here to Mumbai, then Mumbai to Riyadh.

1812
02:07:10,833 --> 02:07:14,540
You'll get the boarding passes to Riyadh
at the Mumbai International airport.

1813
02:07:14,625 --> 02:07:17,915
You'll have to check in your bags again
at Mumbai airport.

1814
02:07:18,000 --> 02:07:19,124
Okay.

1815
02:07:20,916 --> 02:07:22,540
I have another request.

1816
02:07:23,250 --> 02:07:25,249
These three seats together.

1817
02:07:25,333 --> 02:07:26,749
And these two seats behind them.

1818
02:07:26,916 --> 02:07:28,290
Okay, ma'am.

1819
02:07:35,166 --> 02:07:36,540
Done?

1820
02:07:43,500 --> 02:07:44,332
Come on, then.

