02:07:49,166 --> 02:07:50,749
It happens every time.

1822
02:07:50,916 --> 02:07:53,374
Someone takes my window seat.

1823
02:07:53,541 --> 02:07:54,374
Excuse me.

1824
02:07:54,541 --> 02:07:56,624
- Hello.
- Yes.

1825
02:07:56,708 --> 02:07:58,249
That's my seat.

1826
02:08:00,875 --> 02:08:02,249
So sorry.

1827
02:08:12,500 --> 02:08:14,332
